Package org.thymeleaf.expression

Class Messages

  • Object
    • org.thymeleaf.expression.Messages
  • public class Messages
extends Object

    Expression Object for retrieving externalized/internationalized messages from inside Thymeleaf Standard Expressions.

    An object of this class is usually available in variable evaluation expressions with the name #messages.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Daniel Fernández
